DocumentDirectoryEntry	control	Control the processing of the directory entry (e.g. suspend)		controlDocumentDirectoryEntry		Request specific processing (e.g. suspend, skip, terminate)
DocumentDirectoryEntry	exchange	Accept, verify, confirm details about a directory entry		exchangeDocumentDirectoryEntry		Handle an external exchange (e.g. accept, reject, verify) 
